Welcome to CPS  
 Comprehensive Pharmacy Services (CPS) is the nation's leading pharmacy services provider to acute care & specialty hospitals and behavioral systems - delivering pharmacy service value through financial, operational, clinical, therapeutic, and regulatory expertise. 


  


  


   
  
    
  
       

    
    
      
  
